### How to use

1. Clone this repo
2. Hard symlink to /bin -- I symlink to ~/.local/bin/menu
   
   ```ln -s [TARGETPATH]/menu [CLONEDPATH]/menu```

3. Add execution permissions

   ```chmod +x [TARGETPATH]/menu```

4. Add to PATH

    ```PATH=$PATH:[TARGETPATH]```
